title: One Sword Reigns Supreme – Manhuaus
summary: The family elders, fighting for the right to exploit the mines, sent someone to crush his dantian, and became an abandoned son of the Ye family. However, he accidentally entered the Tower of Boundless Hell because of his mother’s bleeding ring and was instructed by a mysterious person to cultivate the Dao of the sword, which no one had ever cultivated before. Ye family abandoned son Ye Xuan: “I must become strong so that I can protect my sister and take back everything I lost in the Ye family.” Mysterious woman: “Follow me and I’ll make you the strongest swordsman in all the heavens.” With the help of the mysterious woman, could Ye Xuan become the strongest swordsman in the realm of the heavens?
